definitions.definition: A sex organ leading from the vulval vestibule / urogenital sinus to the cervix of the uterus for copulation and birth in female therian mammals .

subdefinitions.definition: A similar part in some invertebrates and non-mammalian amniotes .

definitions.definition: A sheathlike structure, such as the leaf of a grass that surrounds a stem .
The vulva , or collectively, the vulva and the vaginal passage.
A coward ; a weakling ; a pussy .
The anus of a trans woman .
